      "message": "#deploy Redesign guild join messages with canvas cards\n\nReplace the plain embed-style `guildCreate` messages with generated canvas welcome cards for both eligible and ineligible servers. The new cards add branded styling, server/bot stats, owner/footer details, and a dedicated “not enough members” layout showing required vs current members, while keeping the support guild link action row via `linkButton`. #deploy",
